name: LPC_Ai_Lumi by Virtuals
description: LUMI is a community-driven digital asset project that integrates NFTs, metaverse culture, and social fan engagement within the Virtuals Protocol ecosystem. Built on the BASE blockchain, LUMI aims to explore new forms of identity expression and interaction through gamified experiences, digital collectibles, and on-chain participation incentives. It is designed to create value through creative storytelling and decentralized user engagement.
